Dear {!Name},
Greetings from Runwal Enterprises!
Your request for change of phone number has been successfully processed and updated in our system. The update was validated through a two-step OTP verification process for security.
Please find the updated details below:
Previous Phone Number: {!Previous_Mobile_Number__c}
Updated Phone Number: {!Mobile_Number__c}
If you notice any discrepancy or did not authorize this request, please contact our customer support team immediately.
Thank you for your continued trust in Runwal Enterprises.
Warm regards, Runwal Enterprises {!$Label.Support_Email} | {!$Label.Support_Phone}
